                <head>Wilson Female College</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <transcript>
                    <p/>
                </transcript>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>The Chairman of the Advisory Committee of Wilson Female College announces
                    that the school is close to opening. He complains only that the citizens of
                    Chambersburg have thus far subscribed no more than $5,000 to the school.
                    Greencastle had offered $15,000 or $20,000. Figures closer to those numbers
                    would ensure its speedy opening.</summary>
                <note/>
